Welcome to the **Employee Management System** project, designed to help businesses streamline and simplify their HR processes. With a solid architecture and modern tech stack, this app ensures that managing employee data, roles, and permissions is a breeze. Letâ€™s take a deep dive into the tech stack and features that power this system! ğŸš€

